# Booking form endpoint — leave blank for local-only demo mode.
#
# Easiest setup (Formspree, free tier):
#   1. Create a free account at https://formspree.io
#   2. Create a new form, copy the endpoint URL
#   3. Set it below, e.g.:
#        VITE_BOOKING_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/abcd1234
#
# Alternatives that accept the same JSON POST shape:
#   - Web3Forms       https://web3forms.com
#   - Getform         https://getform.io
#   - Your own        any endpoint that accepts POST application/json
#
# In Vercel: Project Settings → Environment Variables → add VITE_BOOKING_ENDPOINT
# Variables that start with VITE_ are exposed to the client at build time.
VITE_BOOKING_ENDPOINT=
